name: Diamond & Crossbones Hoodie (Heather/Dark Grey)
description: This is the COMFIEST! SOFTEST! MOST AMAZING! hoodie you will ever put on. In fact so comfy you probably won't ever take it off. It'll kind of become like your favorite blanket as a child. You and your Diamond and Crossbones hoodie will travel the world together, have picnics together and of course keep each other warm. This hoodie might make your girlfriend/boyfriend jealous! P.S. I also heard this hoodie resists vampire bites! 100% Ultra soft cotton! Heather grey hoodie with dark grey print. Comes in Both: Mens and Womens sizes. MADE IN THE USA Pictured: Mike Zeiler of HAVE IDEA!
